name: Cute new PINK SKIN for Iphone 4/ Iphone 5!! Limited edition!
description:
I am offering a super girly cute skin for a limited time!! only making 20 total skins then they will be discontinued!! Its a full phone wrap and super cute!! If you don't know ...  SKINS are a durable way to add style to cell phones, while also offering a small amount of protection. They are not the same as cell phone cases, which are usually more focused on function and less on style. The skins attach directly to the surface of the cell phone and make it possible to achieve a more unique look than most cases can manage. Its basically a sticker that goes on the back of the phone, but a really good vinyl quality. :) The protective skins can be easily applied and repositioned with no air bubbles, removed and reused without leaving any trace of adhesive - even after seven years. 
Controltac graphic film technology is pressure-activated, allowing the skin to be easily applied, repositioned, removed and reused on other devices without a loss of adhesive integrity.
